name: Touch
description:
I feel you near.

Process: A Sony KV-13FM12, Sony HVC-2400, Sony XV-5000 and Panasonic WJ-MX50A dreaming of each other, through each other; reaching. Direct capture reprocessed via Panasonic WJ-MX50A and played back through a Sony KV-13FM12, rescanned via Nikon D7100 donning a Carl Zeiss Jena Biometar 2.8/80.
